  <title>GLib.file_read_link</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function file_read_link(filename: String): String {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_file_read_link()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Reads the contents of the symbolic link <code>filename</code> like the POSIX
readlink() function.  The returned string is in the encoding used
for filenames. Use <link xref="GLib.filename_to_utf8"/> to convert it to UTF-8.</p>
  <p>Since 2.4</p>
<terms>
<item>
<title><code>filename</code></title>
  <p>the symbolic link</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>Returns</code></title>
  <p>A newly-allocated string with the contents of the symbolic link,
         or <code>null</code> if an error occurred.</p>
</item>
